data.description: Price reduced for quick sale. With 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and open floor plans, this house is nested in a quiet street. This house has an abundance of natural light, a large sized dining room, and a big backyard with plenty of trees. This place could be a perfect home for anyone looking for their ideal everyday residence.
